warnings.summary: Submitting this import will duplicate data. All 14 values measure the same quantity at the same time as an existing value in the study.
warnings.resolution: This happens when your import matches line names in the study, but similar values exist under an assay with a different name. You can 1) make identifiers in your file match study assay names, 2) remove study measurements with the same protocol, time, and measurement type as the file, or 3) continue with creating duplicates.
